  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND SECTION 23-15-805, MISSISSIPPI CODE OF 1972, TO MODIFY THE CAMPAIGN FINANCE REPORTING PROCESS BY REQUIRING THAT THE SECRETARY OF STATE MAINTAIN A CENTRAL SITE ON THE INTERNET TO MAKE CAMPAIGN FINANCE REPORTS ACCESSIBLE TO THE PUBLIC AND EASILY SEARCHABLE; TO PROVIDE THAT CANDIDATES, CANDIDATE COMMITTEES AND POLITICAL COMMITTEES MAY FILE REPORTS USING THE ONLINE FILING SYSTEM CREATED BY THE SECRETARY OF STATE; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
